Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天為大家轉播來自永不凋零的櫻花樹所在小島的報導
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤井小姐  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我在初音島為大家帶來報導
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----Title-----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:31.47,title,NTP,0,0,0,,Da Capo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒冷的日子還在繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花一直在綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都搞不清楚春天什麼時候來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快走就趕不上巴士了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  學長  葛木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要到畢業典禮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日子過得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到畢業典禮  就是畢業派對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露姐最近也好像忙著做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業派對特刊該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後也從立夏姐那裡聽說了小櫻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再繼續調查永不凋零的櫻花  實在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這件事放一放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的傍晚  究竟會有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（明天傍晚  來看看永不凋零的櫻花樹…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  之前收到的郵件的謎題還沒有解開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那條寫著「當櫻花盛開之時  在約定的那個地方…」的郵件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得應該和這一連串神秘郵件有某種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得只要弄明白昨天收到的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能解開之前收到的郵件的謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說一切都會在今天傍晚揭曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這只是我的感覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定真像清隆說的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實關於畢業派對特刊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事的話  剛才已經和大家討論過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到櫻的事  我們覺得應該從別的方向寫報導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得那兩人有古怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從小櫻那件事之後  該說是距離突然縮短了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於今年的畢業派對  誰有建議…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛  真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請講  立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏  找回平時的感覺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近都無精打采的  讓我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想你剛經歷過小櫻的事  會那樣也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近就那麼奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要說奇怪的話以前就很奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這話是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算啦算啦  不過我們也馬上就要畢業了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒剩多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然必須在畢業之前搞清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yahoo  小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  露露姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是往常的身體交流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  所以說在學校要自重一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在家就可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家的哪裡可以  起居室？被窩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說…浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是願不願意的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  姬乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙羅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙羅才是怎麼了  找我有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長  放學後還能來看我揮棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揮棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壘球部的…不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也想去看你揮棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過今天放學後大家要去郵件中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  今天的沙羅有點奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻走了之後  你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嘛  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  寂寞的時候不用客氣  隨時跟我說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你想看  裸體圍裙隨時為你奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裸體…圍裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不純潔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.56,MSG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(96,303)\frz23.062}在中庭等你。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才抱歉了  感覺那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說有事…是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那樣盯著人家看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥對誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小隆在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露姐  你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小隆喜歡的是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  夏露露姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只顧著夏露露同學  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  大家都在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不純潔！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你很累的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是在走廊被夏露露學姐抱住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後也收到沙羅同學揮棒的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還遭到葵同學誘惑  更在中庭和姬乃同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是跟蹤狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你剛才的嘆氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我該選擇誰呢  好迷茫啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  竟然能為這種事煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好羨慕你這個幸福的奢侈混蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好羨慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上沒來得及給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在屋頂吃飯  還有點冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許抱怨  這樣就暖和了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人看到我們這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆會困擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是接過吻的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  啊…立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏  能問你一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於櫻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…雖然我說不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知道為什麼  我總覺得還能見到櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏  你知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…關於前世的記憶之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼覺得會和我的前世有關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為…立夏你和櫻相遇後就恢復了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想是不是和立夏的過去有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且關於櫻  你好像也知道一些我不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想聽嗎  我前世的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那該從哪裡說起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我可是被稱為孤高的洋蘭  Category5的魔法使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法解決的事件之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起了許多有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想聽我和清隆初次結合的那個夜晚的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的清隆十分雄偉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  不是那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事知道了又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見  芳乃清隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們最近好像只顧著一名叫櫻的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顧新聞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  用不著你們費心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們忘了嗎  我們的勝負還沒決出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒決出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要真的忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負什麼的已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧  清隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  我不允許你們自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小隆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為你和誰在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了  立夏  一個人獨佔小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然之前一直忍著沒問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來小隆你的心意究竟在誰身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在問小隆你選誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事確實應該說清楚比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連立夏你也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  你到底選誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  杉並大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們完全被她們放置Play了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部員一號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敗給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小隆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要來到這裡就沒事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續剛才的話題…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在立夏的過去中  櫻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆你選誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這件事很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的不是過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起了什麼事情啊  過去是怎樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實在的  這種事怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  只有立夏你一個人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾嗎  說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就算知道這些事情  未來的發展也不一定一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那樣多無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿著早已知道結局的路線行走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是櫻自己所選擇的路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也是時候做出自己的選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的清隆是如何看待我的  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…這是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心意不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我作為現在的我  真的喜歡清隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  清隆你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說清隆  我們來接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清隆你自己說的  下次要徵求你的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是說過  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  這樣就和之前一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次清隆你要主動親我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  讓我們找好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  這件事對我們來說是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆你選誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說錯什麼話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這樣算不上回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺白緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種猶豫不決的地方正是清隆的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確有哥哥的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好  好久不見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者  「初次見面」更好些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  感覺好像不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  剛剛你說「初次見面」…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是  芳乃櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  另一個我承蒙大家照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「另一個我」？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在別的地方也相遇過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你們的反應  果然沒有記憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有…記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所記得的是和你們共同度過的美好時光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及最後一刻所做的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「當櫻花盛開之時  在約定的那個地方…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這封郵件是你發的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然花了些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過又能見到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼  有股很懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是  從剛剛開始就一直這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什麼原因  非常的懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我和清隆一起睡的次數是最多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(170,350)}小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(68,350)}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(491,350)}清隆同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(584,350)}不純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆還是這麼有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  你到底知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能不能聽聽我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事也許有點長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽完的話  所有的疑問都會得到解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  剛好有點心在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  這是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能做到這種程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是讓人綻放笑容的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  就請各位聽我道來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個少女和一棵櫻花樹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個約定和小小的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及無論經過幾十年  幾百年都不會改變的  重要的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論四季幾度輪迴  春天終將到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶來新鮮的櫻花花香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此  宛如Da Capo般循環往復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}Da Capo：音樂符號中的返始，指演奏樂章至符號後歸回最初並再次重複
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同夢一般的夢境的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起始的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:13.02,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この世界はいつも  移り変わってしまうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.03,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここにボクらが存在コトだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.03,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs10\pos(130,0)}いる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:27.63,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}変えようのない１つの現実
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:32.19,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな時代を生き抜いても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:43.36,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにある笑顔をボクは信じていくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:50.70,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}会いたいよ  会いたいよ  またどこかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:56.24,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そう願うのは  ボクのワガママ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:01.06,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}会いたいよ  会いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:09.45,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}またその手であたためて欲しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:13.02,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}雖然這個世界總是在改變著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.03,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}唯獨我們所在的此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:27.63,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}是不容改變的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:32.19,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}無論身處什麼時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:43.36,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的笑容  都是我的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:50.70,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好想見你  好想見你  我們何處再會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:56.24,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這份願望是我的任性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:01.06,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好想見你  好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:09.45,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好希望你再次用這雙手溫暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在問我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.73,0:22:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的胭脂紅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你一樣  非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這個是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是櫻花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  雖然是沒見過的品種
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻…花
